@startuml
' Caption: Session lifecycle based on SessionStatus, with optional cached summary availability.
title Session State Machine

[*] --> Created : create session
Created --> Active : StartSession
Active --> Ended : EndSession
Active --> Ended : timeout / forced stop
Ended --> Archived : archive transcript\n+ artifacts
Archived --> SummaryAvailable : RequestSummary\n(cache summary)
state Archived
state SummaryAvailable
SummaryAvailable --> [*]
Archived --> [*]

note right of Archived
  Derived from persisted transcript and replay artefacts.
  Summary generation is optional and cached on demand.
end note

note right of SummaryAvailable
  Optional derived state that indicates a cached summary exists.
  The DB enum remains SessionStatus.Ended.
end note
@enduml